embeds.description:
**SERVER RULES**

**#1: Mind your Language**
*Slurs of any type are not allowed.  Language that may not be appropriate for some age groups will not be tolerated. Do not attempt to bypass auto-filters.*

**#2: NO Advertising**
*Advertising isn't allowed anywhere*

**#3: Don't post malicious links or files that can steal information.**
*Refrain from posting unknown/unfamiliar links too.*

**#4: Use the proper channels**
*Don't do bot commands in general chat. Keep random images in media. There's usually a channel for everything, so keep it in the designated channel.*

**#5: Be kind**
*Don't harass other users or be toxic. If you don't get along with someone just ignore them and move on.*

**#6: No Spamming**
*Don't spam messages, images, or any other things. This includes wall/large messages, copy and pasted messages, large afks, or any other obnoxious messages.*

 **#7: No NSFW Content**
*Any NSFW content will not be allowed. Keep discussions clean, and suitable for all age groups. This includes emojis, gifs, words, and photos.*

**#8: Don't ask for Personal Information**
*Don't ask for private information, whether its passwords, birth dates, names, etc.*

**#9: Don't abuse spoilers**
*Please do not send messages where you pretend to say a bad word. Don't spam spoilers.*

**#10:Don't ping PEOPLE / ROLES for no reason**
*Refrain from pinging people without a reason. If you need to interact with a user in bot commands, try typing out their name.*

 **#11: Don't use alts maliciously**
*Don't join giveaways to give yourself an unfair advantage. Don't use them to bypass punishments given on a main account.*

**#12: Use common sense**
*Always think before you act. If you aren't sure about something, ask first. Don't be weird towards people, act mature.*

**#13: Stay on topic in each channel.**
*Do not use channels for something other than their intended purpose. Checkout channel topic for more info about the particular channel.*

**#14: Don't try to act smart and BAIT.**
*Please do not send messages where you pretend to say a bad word and try to bait*

**#15 : Don't be dumb and Follow Discord TOS**
*The title is self explanatory*

**#16: DONT USE THE BLACKLISTED WORDS**
*Blacklisted words include but are not limited to the n-word , fa-word , tr-word and any variations of these words.* *Usage of Racial Slurs are not tolerated*


**READ THIS**
*This list does not constitute the full set of rules, and our Staff members may take action on misbehavior and violations that are not explicitly listed above. Repeated offenses after a warning from a Staff member may result in a mute or even ban from the server. At all times, use common sense and good judgement for any action you're about to take.*

<a:tickup:774207637184839680> **Support?** 
*If you have questions , queries or a need to report a person feel free to open a ticket in <#797859426823962644> and ask! :D*
